    ⚡ HOW THE PROGRAM WORKS:
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    
    🔹 CORE TECHNOLOGY
    Tarefas SP operates through a cloud-synchronized task management engine that keeps your tasks updated across all devices. The application uses a local database for offline access with automatic cloud synchronization when connectivity is restored. It features an intuitive drag-and-drop interface, smart categorization, deadline tracking, and collaboration tools. The software is optimized for Brazilian Portuguese with localized date formats, holidays, and business culture considerations .
    
    🔹 KEY FEATURES AT A GLANCE
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    📋 TASK CREATION         │ Create and organize tasks quickly
    🏷️ CATEGORIZATION        │ Tag and filter tasks by project
    ⏰ DEADLINE TRACKING     │ Never miss important dates
    🔔 REMINDERS             │ Custom notifications and alerts
    👥 TEAM COLLABORATION    │ Share tasks with colleagues
    📊 PROGRESS TRACKING     │ Visual task completion status
    ☁️ CLOUD SYNC            │ Access tasks anywhere
    📱 MOBILE COMPANION      │ Manage tasks on the go
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    
    🔹 TASK MANAGEMENT

    📋 CORE FUNCTIONALITY
    • QUICK ADD: Rapid task entry with natural language processing
    • SUBTASKS: Break complex tasks into manageable steps
    • PRIORITY LEVELS: High, medium, low priority indicators
    • DUE DATES: Calendar integration for deadline management
    • REPEATING TASKS: Daily, weekly, monthly recurrence
    • ATTACHMENTS: Add files, images, and links to tasks
    
    🔹 ORGANIZATION

    🏷️ CATEGORIZATION TOOLS
    • PROJECT FOLDERS: Group tasks by project or area
    • CUSTOM TAGS: Create personalized labeling system
    • FILTERS: View tasks by status, priority, or date
    • SEARCH: Full-text search across all tasks
    • SAVED VIEWS: Save custom filter combinations
    • SMART LISTS: Automatic task grouping (Today, Overdue, etc.)
    
    🔹 COLLABORATION

    👥 TEAM FEATURES
    • TASK ASSIGNMENT: Assign tasks to team members
    • COMMENTS: Discuss tasks within the app
    • ATTACHMENTS: Share files with collaborators
    • ACTIVITY LOG: See who did what and when
    • TEAM DASHBOARD: Overview of team progress
    • PERMISSIONS: Control access levels
    
    🔹 VISUALIZATION

    📊 PROGRESS TRACKING
    • KANBAN BOARD: Visual workflow management
    • CALENDAR VIEW: See tasks on a calendar
    • TIMELINE: Gantt-style project timeline
    • COMPLETION RATE: Percentage of tasks done
    • PRODUCTIVITY REPORTS: Personal and team analytics
    • EXPORT: Generate PDF/Excel reports
    
    🔹 NOTIFICATIONS

    🔔 REMINDER SYSTEM
    • EMAIL ALERTS: Receive task reminders via email
    • DESKTOP NOTIFICATIONS: Pop-up reminders
    • PUSH NOTIFICATIONS: Mobile alerts
    • CUSTOM SCHEDULES: Set reminder timing
    • SNOOZE: Postpone reminders when busy
    
